title.rendered: TAJ777 NEWS Bat Sponsorship Deal With Salem Spartans in TNPL 2022

content.rendered:
Ever since the T20 format has come into play, IPL and similar events have made the T20 format even crazier than ever. And why not, when people are ready to adopt the format with open arms.

As IPL started from 2008, there are many other regional leagues for example Tamil Nadu Cricket League which is active since 2016 to promote domestic cricket with its talent. The Tamil Nadu Cricket League (TNPL) was inaugurated by MS Dhoni.

For an update, the Salem Spartans, one of the eight teams in the TNPL, have added a slew of sponsors to their squad for a fruitful season. One of the latest additions that the franchise Salem Spartans has added to their list is a bat sponsorship deal with Taj 777 News in TNPL.

Taj777News will also be the associate partner of TNPL and will be taking responsibility for displaying all the latest updates coming from the franchise in the form of videos, commentary, news etc.

As an additive, Taj 777News will also display articles and coverage through its digital app platform containing useful statistics and rankings of your favorite team or player. However, as we talked about the group of sponsors, the list goes on and on. Vision11, India’s fastest growing fantasy platform with over 5M users, has been announced as an associate sponsor of Salem Spartan, which is India’s biggest sport gaming platform. Under this app you can get all game details as well as user can create their own team of real-life players from upcoming matches, field performance, score points etc.

On the list, Freyer International is another sponsor that Salem Spartans has added to its team as a logistics partner. As a sponsor, Fryer International will be responsible for providing solutions related to international forwarding, logistics and overall supply chain management.

As the title sponsors, the Salem Spartans have chosen SKYEXCH.net as their one stop solution for all sports related updates.

With eight teams, the Tamil Nadu Cricket League is all set to launch its most awaited league run from June 23 to July 31, 2022, in its sixth edition of this season (2022). Cricket format will be T20.

Salem Spartans Playing XI Team (2022)

Darryl Ferrario (Captain), Vijay Shankar, Murugan Ashwin, Akshay Srinivasan, S Abhishek, Vijay Shankar, M Ganesh Murthy, S Bupalan, Umashankar Sushil, Ravi Karthikeyan, Lokesh Raj, Gopinath, G Periyaswamy, B Praneesh, A Arif, AVR Ratnam, G Kishore, M Sugnesh, Abhinav Vishnu, Shubham Mehta, M Vijay Kumar, Rajendran Karthikeyan, Shubham Mehta
